{"tid":770863,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【內地客走貨】栢景臺樓王勁劈500萬易手 低估值17%","createTime":"2018-08-07T12:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T14:25:13.000Z","uid":174649,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"236a973c9b6e87cf08b1057f6401416e5d6aaff6","tid":770863,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180807/large/1533643707_36ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180807%2Flarge%2F1533643707_36ab.jpg&h=6ae30298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中原地產陳家鴻表示，北角栢景臺剛劈價成交，1座高層B室全海景樓王，實用面積998方呎，業主為內地客，叫價3,800萬元放盤，最終疑急套現，減價500萬至3,300萬元易手，呎價33,066元，較估值低最多676萬元或17%。中銀及滙豐銀行網上估值3,618萬及3,976萬元。原業主2013年2月以2,950萬元買入單位，5年升值僅12%"},{"pid":"ccdc267fc59585dac047f6bcedd5ba71bffdc22c","tid":770863,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"減完都3000萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9135936e499fcb83af187a9e59f66e254cbea39","tid":770863,"uid":178317,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:37:33.000Z","msg":"劈完都3300萬,香港真係癲㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5926dd8cb9f3ccc18f6cc28f139cfe99e1c3b5b","tid":770863,"uid":51521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"第一滴血"},{"pid":"8275e53e62ef496604b4f6fc46bdc262e03ac42a","tid":770863,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老味"},{"pid":"f65456adaa4227c39465d9c242ecf1bcbd2c262a","tid":770863,"uid":37979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"贏國真係又贏， 去走先賺先， 等你班香港傻仔接火捧。係減咗價， 不過出到貨先係真金白銀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c83baa0cc58f44094be2bcf46898743aa2f6139","tid":770863,"uid":511,"like